### **For Developers - Quick Start**

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/andrewk529/mak-platform.git
cd mak-platform

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your configuration

# Start development server
npm start

# Run tests
npm test

# Deploy to testnet
npm run deploy:testnet
```

